  "keyFeatures": [
    "FIFO ticket-ordered queue with live position tracking",
    "Auto-admission via browser polling — no refresh required",
    "Skip-the-line paid queue jumping with configurable per-position pricing",
    "Surge pricing via RateFunc — price scales with queue depth",
    "Time-limited VIP passes that auto-promote clients across queue re-entries",
    "Edge-triggered lifecycle callbacks (EventFull, EventDrain, EventEnter, EventExit, etc.) for autoscaling and observability",
    "Background reaper that evicts abandoned tokens and prevents ghost-ticket queue stalls",
    "Max queue depth circuit breaker to protect memory under extreme load",
    "Runtime capacity adjustment via SetCap — no restart required",
    "Configurable cookie security (HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite, Path, Domain)",
    "Sub-3μs fast path; sub-nanosecond QueueDepth and UtilizationSmoothed reads",
    "Drop-in single-import integration — one Init, one RegisterRoutes"
  ],
